      public void updateAndMoveClassifier(long id, String name, long oldParentId, long newParentId)
      Edit (and move, if oldParentId != newParentId) a classifier that contains other classifiers or patterns. The classifier keeps all its patterns or child classifiers.
      Parameters:
      id - Classifier identifier
      name - Edited name of classifier
      oldParentId - Old parent classifier identifier (-1 means root classifier)
      newParentId - New parent classifier identifier (-1 means root classifier)
